<br>
<br>
Levitate - Levitate does not function at all within PoS. <br>
<br>
Gates of All Types - No type of gate spells work in PoS. This includes gate, evacs, succors, etc. Probably Translocate as well. <br>
<br>
Bind - You cannot bind in PoS. <br>
<br>
Call of the Hero - CotH does not work in PoS. <br>
<br>
Eye of Zomm - supposedly works differently, though I don't know how. Possibly allows movement in 3 dimensions. <br>
<br>
Pet Summons - Mages may only summon air pets, which will appear as small Djinnis as opposed to their normal look. Necromancer pets are functional, but severely disempowered. It is rumored that they hit like a level 1, which is unlikely, but needless to say they are much less effective. Shaman and Enchanter pets function normally.<br>
